data.description: Very charming two story home located just outside Lancaster in Lampeter-Strasburg Schools.  Spacious living room with wood-burning fireplace and beautiful hardwood flooring.  Lots of old world charm like wood doors and trim, with modern touches that include a recently renovated kitchen with new cabinets and countertops.  Finished lower level with one car garage!  Relax on the porch and enjoy the large backyard.  Walk to the park or Pickle Ball courts, golf and downtown Lancaster are just a short drive away.  Schedule your showing today!
